{"tid":1813550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最新情況：武漢市肺炎病例群組個案","createTime":"2020-01-06T11:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T11:39:36.000Z","uid":268519,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fef9c1a66e5f2c32073346d2651e14d339498775","tid":1813550,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:01:31.000Z","msg":"自2019年12月31日起，衞生署衞生防護中心共接獲<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">21宗</span></strong>加強監測個案的報告，而患者最近<ins>曾到訪湖北省武漢巿</ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(截至2020年1月6日中午12時)</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n個案詳情如下: <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K8e7akH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK8e7akH.png&h=d013a270&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OAWxmsn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOAWxmsn.png&h=7b417583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/enhanced_sur_pneumonia_wuhan_chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2Fenhanced_sur_pneumonia_wuhan_chi.pdf&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=83fd7b44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/enhanced_sur_pneumonia_wuhan_chi.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n每日去個網睇下有冇update<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jVUnJGR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjVUnJGR.png&h=5db49ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/tc/features/102465.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ffeatures%2F102465.html&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=aa92e2c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/tc/features/102465.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戴口罩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"225e788d9c3735a397df3d63723d6441431ffd0c","tid":1813550,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:01:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf2aa3b406b758ef4107021a53781cd9609bde57","tid":1813550,"uid":268519,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:02:42.000Z","msg":"一號女咁耐都未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72710005168e216e9d591d3519f2b80f327998ad","tid":1813550,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:03:27.000Z","msg":"點解會單方向散播疫情, 會唔會真是生化武器嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#33<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">Joshua</span></strong><br />\n支那用瘟疫屠殺香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>依家所有武漢資訊都係比支共操控<br />\n聲稱有59人中招隔離<br />\n做樣封個野味市場<br />\n網上五毛扮屋企人話失聯話有人死<br />\n全部都係支共一手操控<br />\n冇其他人證明到，冇化驗結果，冇外國認證<br />\n<br />\n到香港<br />\n所有所謂防疫工作係建基於支那操控嘅資訊，結果隔離咁多個人仲未有野搵到<br />\n<br />\n假疫情對支共同港共都有利<br />\n支共:<br />\n威脅美國同其他國家自己有生化武器輸出<br />\n扮弱者疫情大國唔會比人打，兼有援助<br />\n清除異己，反對就會被病死<br />\n加強對香港控制而不被世界非議<br />\n<br />\n港共:<br />\n利用市民怕沙士來恐嚇市民<br />\n減少示威活動<br />\n利用防疫政策去對付示威者</blockquote>"},{"pid":"73ff860b777730c5c221f7b09d3f226d736dd3c2","tid":1813550,"uid":241567,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:14:15.000Z","msg":"睇番紀錄大部分都係甲型流感<br />\n而未明朗既得5個<br />\n可否解讀武漢肺炎 傳播力唔係想像中高 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a0448e319ef40622cc0a1f67d120f7bcf77222","tid":1813550,"uid":241567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:15:10.000Z","msg":"會唔會甲型流感仲危險過（傳播性） 武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"941d9c86e34a615be2e8e0f8905a225a890d65dc","tid":1813550,"uid":244230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:29:53.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"20fad7fd7ddff35bb85edaabb89c14ad673c4996","tid":1813550,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"